    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hmm, interesting. We use React internally for the rendering, and it uses `div`s internally. This might conflict with its internal validation when using it to render inside a `table`.\n\nI think #707 would fix this issue as well, by letting you handle the whole rendering loop yourself in Hogan without needing React for each individual hit.\n\nThis is definitely a valid concern. @bobylito any idea on how to tell React to render a loop inside a `table` as a workaround until #707 is fixed?\n",
