    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This may be easily solved if react implements the \"fragment\" api: https://github.com/facebook/react/issues/2127. \n\nIn the meantime, follow #707 for a way to use tables in the hits widget.\n\nAlso, most widgets having both container and `items` template should support tables\n",
